     C* D2: numeric data-structure subfield decode-on-read. Writing ASCII
     C* '1234' through alphameric subfield CHRS must decode to 1234 when
     C* read through the overlapping numeric subfield NUM.
     I            DS
     I                                        1   4 CHRS
     I                                        1   40NUM
     C                     MOVEL'1234'    CHRS
     C           NUM       COMP 1234                     10
     C  10                 Z-ADD1         RPGRET
